I'm an experienced detective.

51:16.058 --> 51:19.101
So guess what I detected.

51:19.269 --> 51:20.478
What?

51:20.645 --> 51:24.023
That she's in love
with her own body.

51:24.191 --> 51:26.901
Makes her dizzy with excitement.

51:30.655 --> 51:32.573
