52:12.614 --> 52:13.864
Did you learn it at school?

52:14.032 --> 52:15.866
The hard school. Family life.

52:16.034 --> 52:18.786
- But you keep cheerful.
- You've got it, I keep cheerful.

52:18.954 --> 52:21.455
I've got an optimistic nature.

52:21.623 --> 52:24.166
You got to when you're a policeman.
Otherwise, you'd go mad.

52:24.334 --> 52:27.711
No, I'll tell you
what keeps me going.

52:29.381 --> 52:33.050
