55:03.994 --> 55:06.161
Bollocks. You're a joker, all right.

55:06.329 --> 55:07.871
A real joker.

55:08.039 --> 55:09.832
Come on, we're off to the station.

55:10.000 --> 55:12.584
- There's something very wrong here.
