56:31.623 --> 56:34.792
Entirely my own idea.

56:34.959 --> 56:37.961
This is a game between us, old boy.

56:38.129 --> 56:40.964
Between you and me.

56:41.132 --> 56:43.634
Don't forget, I'm half Italian.

56:43.802 --> 56:45.469
We go in for revenge.

56:58.400 --> 57:02.820
After all, you frightened
