57:09.911 --> 57:12.121
And then you fired.

57:15.959 --> 57:17.584
I don't like guns.

57:18.920 --> 57:20.629
They kill you.

57:23.883 --> 57:25.551
Okay.

57:25.718 --> 57:28.262
